data.description: Welcome to your dream home, nestled in a prime location just minutes away from NAS Pensacola, Big Lagoon State Park, and beautiful white sand beaches. This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick house is situated on a large corner lot adorned with shade trees.  Step inside to discover an inviting floor plan, featuring a living room with a vaulted ceiling and a floor-to-ceiling brick accent wall, complete with a cozy wood-burning fireplace. Ceramic tile with a wood inlay adds a touch of elegance to the living area, while the kitchen and baths offer ceramic tile flooring. The kitchen is a chef's delight, with attractive granite countertops, lots of cabinet space, a built-in microwave, and a charming breakfast nook for casual dining.  Entertaining is a breeze with the 12' x 20' covered back patio, overlooking a fully fenced backyard with a privacy fence and shady oak trees. The property includes an attached two-car garage and a side driveway with a double swing gate for easy access to the impressive 24' x 28' detached two-car garage/workshop. Equipped with power, water, and a full bathroom, this workshop is perfect for the hobbyist or DIY enthusiast.  Plenty of room to park an RV on the paved backyard driveway as well!  With a prime location just minutes from top amenities such as Johnson Beach, Pensacola Beach, Pensacola State College, and the VA clinic, this home is a rare find. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home and start enjoying the best that Pensacola has to offer!
